WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.350
Welcome all of you. Good morning,

00:00:03.350 --> 00:00:03.360
family.

00:00:03.360 --> 00:00:04.990
There

00:00:04.990 --> 00:00:05.000
are

00:00:05.000 --> 00:00:07.030
1,600 of you already. I need to

00:00:07.040 --> 00:00:09.670
start. Good morning, family. Praise the

00:00:09.680 --> 00:00:11.910
Lord. That fan's making me cough,

00:00:11.920 --> 00:00:13.910
baby.

00:00:13.920 --> 00:00:15.910
Thank you for joining us. I appreciate

00:00:15.920 --> 00:00:18.310
it. I have a fan high blowing on me

00:00:18.310 --> 00:00:18.320
because

00:00:18.320 --> 00:00:20.550
these lights are hot and I sweat the

00:00:20.560 --> 00:00:22.110
whole time and I get finished and I'm

00:00:22.120 --> 00:00:24.510
drenched. But

00:00:24.520 --> 00:00:26.150
I'm thankful that every one of you would

00:00:26.160 --> 00:00:28.070
join me so late in the evening. I had a

00:00:28.080 --> 00:00:30.110
lot going on today, and I couldn't

00:00:30.120 --> 00:00:32.790
do a video earlier. So, for the ones

00:00:32.800 --> 00:00:35.390
that want to watch it back, thank you.

00:00:35.960 --> 00:00:37.390
I'm going to pray with you tonight.

00:00:37.400 --> 00:00:39.990
There's a lot on my heart

00:00:40.000 --> 00:00:41.830
and I'm going to go over the things that

00:00:41.840 --> 00:00:43.750
the Lord

00:00:43.760 --> 00:00:46.950
talked to us about last night. Now, I'm

00:00:46.960 --> 00:00:48.590
going to come right out and say it: I'm

00:00:48.600 --> 00:00:51.230
not a financial advisor. I'm not here to

00:00:51.240 --> 00:00:52.990
tell you what to do with your finances.

00:00:53.000 --> 00:00:55.670
I have to say that every single time.

00:00:58.080 --> 00:00:59.670
This is what I've been instructed.

00:00:59.680 --> 00:01:02.510
This is for entertainment purposes only.

00:01:02.520 --> 00:01:04.350
You can do what you want to, but

00:01:04.360 --> 00:01:06.630
I bring this to you for you to pray

00:01:06.640 --> 00:01:07.830
about it.

00:01:07.840 --> 00:01:10.030
This is very serious for what I believe

00:01:10.040 --> 00:01:12.070
the Lord has shown me. But I'm human;

00:01:12.080 --> 00:01:14.510
I can miss it. This is what I believe.

00:01:14.520 --> 00:01:15.710
This is what I believe the Lord has

00:01:15.710 --> 00:01:15.720
shown

00:01:15.720 --> 00:01:18.390
me concerning the finances,

00:01:18.400 --> 00:01:20.870
concerning the world, and what I believe

00:01:20.880 --> 00:01:23.110
the Lord has shown me is what's coming.

00:01:23.120 --> 00:01:24.750
So if you don't believe that and you

00:01:24.760 --> 00:01:26.350
don't believe all these things that I'm

00:01:26.360 --> 00:01:29.110
saying, you take it to God in prayer and

00:01:29.120 --> 00:01:31.230
you see what the Holy Spirit tells

00:01:31.240 --> 00:01:33.910
you. Do not invest in anything based on

00:01:33.920 --> 00:01:36.150
anything that I'm about to say. You take

00:01:36.160 --> 00:01:38.350
it to God in prayer. Okay? That's

00:01:38.360 --> 00:01:40.750
maturity. So you need to be mature

00:01:40.760 --> 00:01:43.910
about this.

00:01:43.920 --> 00:01:47.070
Okay? So last night we

00:01:47.080 --> 00:01:48.390
saw—and

00:01:48.400 --> 00:01:53.150
I want to say

00:01:53.160 --> 00:01:55.750
we give all the glory to God. I have no

00:01:55.760 --> 00:01:58.030
ability on my own to see anything; it's

00:01:58.040 --> 00:02:02.390
all Jesus. And I want to say that

00:02:02.400 --> 00:02:04.230
last night what we saw in prayer was

00:02:04.240 --> 00:02:06.710
pretty cool. I thought we took it and

00:02:06.720 --> 00:02:08.350
we've been praying over it all day, and

00:02:08.360 --> 00:02:10.310
Braden and I have been

00:02:10.320 --> 00:02:12.590
really processing it because when we see

00:02:12.600 --> 00:02:15.230
these things, Braden tries to

00:02:15.240 --> 00:02:17.110
research and see what the Lord's

00:02:17.120 --> 00:02:18.550
showing us and if it's already there in

00:02:18.560 --> 00:02:20.430
the news or

00:02:20.440 --> 00:02:22.590
something that we can prepare

00:02:22.600 --> 00:02:25.070
ourselves for maybe and position

00:02:25.080 --> 00:02:28.670
ourselves to be on the blessing side.

00:02:28.680 --> 00:02:32.190
I saw a new gold rush coming

00:02:32.200 --> 00:02:34.990
and I don't know

00:02:35.000 --> 00:02:37.030
when this thing's going to

00:02:37.040 --> 00:02:39.110
kick off. I believe it's coming and I

00:02:39.120 --> 00:02:41.950
believe in my spirit it's coming soon.

00:02:41.960 --> 00:02:46.190
I saw gold go up like

00:02:46.200 --> 00:02:50.030
this, and it went down

00:02:50.040 --> 00:02:52.950
and it had a dip, but as it went up, it

00:02:52.960 --> 00:02:56.470
went high as a cat's

00:02:56.470 --> 00:02:56.480
back—which

00:02:56.480 --> 00:02:59.190
I know is

00:02:59.190 --> 00:02:59.200
symbolic—but

00:02:59.200 --> 00:03:01.750
it went up really, really high and

00:03:01.760 --> 00:03:03.630
then it started to go down.

00:03:03.640 --> 00:03:06.430
But as it was at its peak,

00:03:06.440 --> 00:03:13.110
I saw people taking their jewelry

00:03:13.120 --> 00:03:16.150
and any kind of gold anything they had,

00:03:16.160 --> 00:03:18.390
and they were trying to get rid of it

00:03:18.400 --> 00:03:21.550
because of the all-time highs of gold

00:03:21.560 --> 00:03:23.550
that I saw that were coming.

00:03:23.560 --> 00:03:26.430
I saw people going in old mines and I

00:03:26.440 --> 00:03:28.230
saw Colorado.

00:03:28.240 --> 00:03:31.350
I saw Utah and parts of California

00:03:31.360 --> 00:03:33.550
where old mines

00:03:33.560 --> 00:03:36.230
were dormant in the hills

00:03:36.240 --> 00:03:38.190
and people were trying to sneak up in

00:03:38.200 --> 00:03:41.470
these mines with little head lanterns on

00:03:41.480 --> 00:03:43.310
and they were looking for any kind of

00:03:43.320 --> 00:03:44.630
scrap,

00:03:44.640 --> 00:03:46.790
little bitty flakes of gold they could

00:03:46.800 --> 00:03:50.630
find to gather up to go and cash them

00:03:50.640 --> 00:03:54.510
in. I saw gold in the vision was over

00:03:54.520 --> 00:03:56.870
$10,000 an ounce.

00:03:56.880 --> 00:03:58.950
And when this happened, I saw the

00:03:58.960 --> 00:04:01.270
people, like I said, looking through

00:04:01.280 --> 00:04:04.630
creek beds in Colorado and places where

00:04:04.640 --> 00:04:07.590
they could pan for gold. And I saw a

00:04:07.600 --> 00:04:10.670
gold rush of people, an excitement

00:04:10.680 --> 00:04:13.190
of realizing if they could just find a

00:04:13.200 --> 00:04:15.910
little, it would get them

00:04:18.000 --> 00:04:19.470
a

00:04:19.480 --> 00:04:21.509
substantial amount of money. An ounce of

00:04:21.519 --> 00:04:23.790
gold was over 10,000. So they were

00:04:23.800 --> 00:04:25.230
just trying to find just a little bit.

00:04:25.240 --> 00:04:27.430
That's several hundred dollars. And for

00:04:27.440 --> 00:04:31.430
some people, $100 a day is a lot.

00:04:31.440 --> 00:04:33.430
So they were down in the creek beds in

00:04:33.440 --> 00:04:36.350
Colorado and these places and streams

00:04:36.360 --> 00:04:38.630
and places in the mountains trying to

00:04:38.640 --> 00:04:41.110
pan for gold just to get

00:04:41.120 --> 00:04:42.830
gold.

00:04:42.840 --> 00:04:45.270
And that's when I saw and I heard 'new

00:04:45.280 --> 00:04:48.910
gold rush'in the headlines.

00:04:48.920 --> 00:04:53.470
And this was worldwide: new gold rush.

00:04:53.480 --> 00:04:55.310
But especially in America, people were

00:04:55.320 --> 00:04:57.990
trying to find old mines and they were

00:04:58.000 --> 00:04:59.750
going in them. It was

00:04:59.760 --> 00:05:02.630
dangerous because they were abandoned and

00:05:02.640 --> 00:05:04.830
there was nobody working

00:05:04.840 --> 00:05:06.990
those anymore.

00:05:06.990 --> 00:05:07.000
After

00:05:07.000 --> 00:05:08.550
years and years of

00:05:08.560 --> 00:05:10.190
abandonment, that's a dangerous

00:05:10.200 --> 00:05:11.950
place to be if there's

00:05:11.960 --> 00:05:14.390
no safety, so they're

00:05:14.400 --> 00:05:16.710
putting their life in danger. But I saw

00:05:16.720 --> 00:05:18.510
them going in there and they were trying

00:05:18.520 --> 00:05:20.550
to hide and go in there and just look

00:05:20.560 --> 00:05:21.790
for anything, digging on the walls,

00:05:21.800 --> 00:05:23.270
trying to find whatever they could to

00:05:23.280 --> 00:05:26.590
find even just a little bit.

00:05:26.600 --> 00:05:28.710
And so I saw that in the vision

00:05:28.720 --> 00:05:30.350
and I thought that was interesting. I

00:05:30.360 --> 00:05:32.430
did not see silver. Now, that doesn't mean silver

00:05:32.430 --> 00:05:32.440
is

00:05:32.440 --> 00:05:34.070
not going to do anything, but I

00:05:34.080 --> 00:05:35.910
did not see silver. I just thought it

00:05:35.920 --> 00:05:37.030
was interesting because the Lord showed me

00:05:37.040 --> 00:05:39.510
gold. I see in part, hear in part.

00:05:39.520 --> 00:05:42.350
But as I was praying into that, I

00:05:42.350 --> 00:05:42.360
saw

00:05:42.360 --> 00:05:49.310
five major honeypots

00:05:49.310 --> 00:05:49.320
and

00:05:49.320 --> 00:05:52.270
a lot of the Body of

00:05:52.280 --> 00:05:54.550
Christ of what I was seeing,

00:05:54.560 --> 00:05:57.830
some of them had one honey pot and

00:05:57.840 --> 00:06:00.830
some of them had more than

00:06:03.080 --> 00:06:06.470
two or three honey pots and they had the

00:06:06.480 --> 00:06:08.750
pots all—and it was honey

00:06:08.760 --> 00:06:10.550
pots. It looked like

00:06:10.550 --> 00:06:10.560
substantial

00:06:10.560 --> 00:06:13.270
something, sugar. It was good,

00:06:13.280 --> 00:06:15.990
like something fun.

00:06:16.000 --> 00:06:18.550
And this was a means of provision of

00:06:18.560 --> 00:06:22.390
wealth transfer. And I saw a pink

00:06:22.400 --> 00:06:24.750
currency

00:06:24.760 --> 00:06:27.190
that was about to go up,

00:06:27.200 --> 00:06:29.990
that was about to be reinstated,

00:06:30.000 --> 00:06:32.630
that was about to have value,

00:06:32.640 --> 00:06:34.430
but it wasn't as much as what people

00:06:34.440 --> 00:06:36.830
had thought it was going to be.

00:06:36.840 --> 00:06:39.110
People were disappointed.

00:06:39.120 --> 00:06:42.150
I saw the Prince of Persia latching

00:06:42.150 --> 00:06:42.160
onto

00:06:42.160 --> 00:06:44.270
Babylon.

00:06:44.280 --> 00:06:47.270
He had his hands on it. And as these

00:06:47.270 --> 00:06:47.280
things—I've

00:06:47.280 --> 00:06:49.630
warned you and warned you

00:06:49.640 --> 00:06:52.270
over the years—what has it been about

00:06:52.280 --> 00:06:54.190
Persia? Even how long ago

00:06:54.200 --> 00:06:56.030
was it when I saw Persia

00:06:56.040 --> 00:06:58.070
grabbing onto it? That

00:06:58.080 --> 00:07:00.230
was back probably in November

00:07:00.240 --> 00:07:02.710
before all this drama going on with

00:07:02.720 --> 00:07:06.790
Iran. Persia was falling apart. And I saw

00:07:06.800 --> 00:07:09.550
the Prince of Persia. He had sweat beads

00:07:09.560 --> 00:07:10.990
going down his face and he was

00:07:11.000 --> 00:07:16.590
straining, losing his grip on Babylon.

00:07:16.600 --> 00:07:19.830
It was coming through his fingers.

00:07:19.840 --> 00:07:23.510
Does anybody remember that?

00:07:23.520 --> 00:07:26.150
When I first was shown that by the Holy

00:07:26.160 --> 00:07:28.190
Spirit, he had a hold of it with his

00:07:28.200 --> 00:07:30.950
fingers and he was squeezing it with all

00:07:30.960 --> 00:07:32.550
he had—the buildings, the

00:07:32.550 --> 00:07:32.560
structure—and

00:07:32.560 --> 00:07:35.150
he was losing his

00:07:35.160 --> 00:07:36.550
grip.

00:07:36.560 --> 00:07:38.470
And the Lord said, 'I'm the one doing

00:07:38.480 --> 00:07:39.750
this.

00:07:39.760 --> 00:07:41.910
He's about to lose his grip over

00:07:41.910 --> 00:07:41.920
Babylon.'And

00:07:41.920 --> 00:07:43.310
Babylon's going to come up out of

00:07:43.320 --> 00:07:45.350
the ashes, the flames.

00:07:45.360 --> 00:07:50.470
And I saw a new stable Babylon coming.

00:07:50.480 --> 00:07:52.430
And when I saw it, palm trees were

00:07:52.440 --> 00:07:54.390
coming up, buildings,

00:07:54.400 --> 00:07:56.550
oil, blessing,

00:07:56.560 --> 00:08:00.350
and a new stable currency.

00:08:00.360 --> 00:08:02.670
I saw a new stable currency. And I saw

00:08:02.680 --> 00:08:05.670
the number 25.

00:08:05.680 --> 00:08:08.550
And it was black with gold around it.

00:08:08.560 --> 00:08:11.350
Does anybody remember the black 25? And I

00:08:11.360 --> 00:08:14.070
said, I keep seeing this 25 come up

00:08:14.080 --> 00:08:15.630
out of the ground. I don't know what

00:08:15.640 --> 00:08:17.910
this is. I still don't.

00:08:17.920 --> 00:08:20.710
I believe it's a rate. I believe

00:08:20.720 --> 00:08:22.550
something about 25. I don't know.

00:08:22.560 --> 00:08:25.430
It was on a

00:08:25.440 --> 00:08:29.230
pink piece of paper, a smaller

00:08:29.230 --> 00:08:29.240
denomination.

00:08:29.240 --> 00:08:31.510
It was a 25 something.

00:08:31.520 --> 00:08:32.950
And I saw it and I thought that was very

00:08:32.960 --> 00:08:34.430
interesting.

00:08:34.440 --> 00:08:37.230
So last night we saw these things

00:08:37.240 --> 00:08:38.630
again.

00:08:38.640 --> 00:08:41.709
But as I was seeing this, I was taken

00:08:41.719 --> 00:08:43.230
to Israel

00:08:43.240 --> 00:08:45.790
and I saw MBS

00:08:45.800 --> 00:08:48.630
leading in a V.

00:08:48.640 --> 00:08:51.550
He was a leader. He was coming

00:08:51.560 --> 00:08:53.910
in there to do things, but he had other

00:08:53.920 --> 00:08:56.870
Arab men behind him kind of like a duck

00:08:56.880 --> 00:08:58.870
formation.

00:08:58.880 --> 00:09:01.230
Whenever you see ducks flying

00:09:01.240 --> 00:09:03.710
and you can see geese flying,

00:09:03.720 --> 00:09:06.390
they fly in a V. Well, he was in a V. He

00:09:06.400 --> 00:09:08.590
was the head of it. And I saw him

00:09:08.600 --> 00:09:10.950
talking and he went into Israel and I

00:09:10.960 --> 00:09:14.190
saw him negotiating Gaza

00:09:14.200 --> 00:09:18.350
with Trump and other

00:09:18.360 --> 00:09:20.070
countries

00:09:20.080 --> 00:09:22.190
and they rebuilt

00:09:22.200 --> 00:09:23.830
Gaza.

00:09:23.840 --> 00:09:27.670
I saw a golf course with Trump's name on

00:09:27.680 --> 00:09:31.270
it that was a Trump golf course with a

00:09:31.280 --> 00:09:35.030
flag in the ninth hole. Now I know this

00:09:35.040 --> 00:09:36.750
is symbolic.

00:09:36.760 --> 00:09:38.390
It's not—God's not just showing me

00:09:38.400 --> 00:09:39.630
the ninth hole. There's something more

00:09:39.640 --> 00:09:41.310
about this there. It's a type

00:09:41.310 --> 00:09:41.320
and

00:09:41.320 --> 00:09:42.510
shadow. There's something to this. It's

00:09:42.520 --> 00:09:43.790
a code.

00:09:43.800 --> 00:09:45.670
So, if you all know codes and dreams and

00:09:45.680 --> 00:09:48.230
visions, I don't. I just see

00:09:48.240 --> 00:09:51.110
this stuff and I pray over it.

00:09:51.120 --> 00:09:53.630
It was a flag that was not a

00:09:53.630 --> 00:09:53.640
normal-looking

00:09:53.640 --> 00:09:55.270
flag, but it looked like a flag

00:09:55.280 --> 00:09:57.670
that you would put in a golf hole.

00:09:57.680 --> 00:10:01.830
It said 'Trump Golf Course

00:10:01.830 --> 00:10:01.840
Gaza,'and

00:10:01.840 --> 00:10:04.990
it was blue and white, which looked

00:10:05.000 --> 00:10:07.110
like Israel.

00:10:07.120 --> 00:10:09.110
Do you know how Israel's flag is blue

00:10:09.120 --> 00:10:12.710
and white? Well, this flag was white

00:10:12.720 --> 00:10:16.510
with blue on it, just like Israel's flag,

00:10:16.520 --> 00:10:20.110
but it had 'Gaza'written on

00:10:20.120 --> 00:10:22.230
it. It was blue and white and

00:10:22.230 --> 00:10:22.240
was at

00:10:22.240 --> 00:10:24.510
the ninth hole.

00:10:24.520 --> 00:10:27.790
It said 'Trump Golf

00:10:27.790 --> 00:10:27.800
Course'in

00:10:27.800 --> 00:10:29.590
beautiful

00:10:29.600 --> 00:10:31.710
cursive writing,

00:10:31.720 --> 00:10:34.670
and it had blue outlining the flag

00:10:34.680 --> 00:10:38.350
just like an Israeli flag.

00:10:39.440 --> 00:10:41.870
I saw the

00:10:41.880 --> 00:10:45.430
green grass on this golf

00:10:45.440 --> 00:10:48.070
course that looked absolutely beautiful,

00:10:48.080 --> 00:10:50.110
and it was next to the Mediterranean

00:10:51.720 --> 00:10:54.510
Sea.

00:10:57.880 --> 00:10:59.590
All of it was blue. I could see the

00:10:59.600 --> 00:11:02.070
water, the golf course,

00:11:02.070 --> 00:11:02.080
and

00:11:02.080 --> 00:11:05.230
beautiful

00:11:05.240 --> 00:11:08.829
mansions behind

00:11:08.829 --> 00:11:08.839
it—I'm

00:11:08.839 --> 00:11:12.510
talking big money homes

00:11:12.520 --> 00:11:14.670
that look like something out of Miami.

00:11:14.680 --> 00:11:16.950
They were white stucco houses with

00:11:16.960 --> 00:11:19.829
rooftops that could look out over

00:11:19.839 --> 00:11:21.270
the water.

00:11:21.280 --> 00:11:22.870
It had a rail

00:11:22.880 --> 00:11:25.590
and seats where you could watch

00:11:25.600 --> 00:11:28.430
the golfers and look at the water.

00:11:28.440 --> 00:11:30.150
It looked like something out of Los

00:11:30.160 --> 00:11:32.110
Angeles or

00:11:32.120 --> 00:11:33.550
Miami; it was absolutely

00:11:33.560 --> 00:11:35.550
beautiful. I

00:11:35.550 --> 00:11:35.560
suddenly saw

00:11:35.560 --> 00:11:39.350
oil

00:11:39.360 --> 00:11:41.950
derricks, and the Lord said, 'Remember

00:11:41.960 --> 00:11:44.190
the Houston Oilers.'I saw the Houston

00:11:44.200 --> 00:11:45.670
Oilers

00:11:45.680 --> 00:11:48.590
and the oil derricks,

00:11:48.600 --> 00:11:52.430
but they were coming up out of Gaza.

00:11:52.440 --> 00:11:55.390
There was a massive amount of money

00:11:55.400 --> 00:11:58.550
in oil and gas underneath the

00:11:58.560 --> 00:12:00.710
soil of Gaza

00:12:00.710 --> 00:12:00.720
and

00:12:00.720 --> 00:12:03.270
underneath the Mediterranean, outside of

00:12:03.280 --> 00:12:04.750
the coastline. I

00:12:04.750 --> 00:12:04.760
saw a

00:12:04.760 --> 00:12:09.190
substantial amount of oil and

00:12:09.200 --> 00:12:10.790
gas.

00:12:10.790 --> 00:12:10.800
Then

00:12:10.800 --> 00:12:13.550
I saw

00:12:13.560 --> 00:12:16.910
